oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mule team
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Five men in hats, plowing with a mule team and sowing sericea lespedeza by hand in Humphreys County, Tenn. A cluster of trees are in the background, and the photograph shows the portion of the field still to be plowed.
